:"2020-12-27T09:24:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32ad6f7279ccd002521a05b6748382d6f9d8f867","tid":2342624,"uid":183383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:31:31.000Z","msg":"你影??"},{"pid":"afaeac2a0e89d241a31ee2b2dc7b787fd5f78a60","tid":2342624,"uid":82917,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"32ad6f7279ccd002521a05b6748382d6f9d8f867","tid":2342624,"uid":183383,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:31:31.000Z","msg":"你影??"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:32:45.000Z","msg":"Fb見到 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19f5567cf6a0f3ac8ed5b615dd676eae2b3db570","tid":2342624,"uid":81684,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T09:33:17.000Z","msg":"唔好笑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n----------------------------簽名檔-------------------------<br />\n仲有班雞蟲走狗(垃圾)<br />\n尤其<span class=\"red\">#5407 早晨歡迎光臨</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢條死垃圾次次比我屌撚到縮返入佢老母塊閪<br />\n唔撚夠講 要折墮到生安白造屈鳩我篤灰國安法<br />\n而家比人踢爆成個局都係木耳編排 仲上嚟讚自己靚仔<br />\n條#5407 早晨歡迎光臨 即刻冇撚曬影<br />\n一早話咗佢係飛機陳 木耳嗰班雞蟲賤種嚟<br />\n條垃圾仲想扮唔識佢兩個 好彩而家總算還我清白<br />\n<br />\n點知<span class=\"red\">#47356 飛雪連天射白濁</span> 出嚟老屈我比木耳屌過<br />\n極度懷疑佢係木耳第五個分身<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n想屈我比木操呃過閪屌 即係屈我係私怨撚 <br />\n侮辱完我貞潔之餘 仲順勢屈我係40路 <br />\n點知比人屌兩屌 條撚樣就柒到縮返入佢老母骨灰<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8MsXyP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8MsXyP.gif&h=f83cf594&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8MsXyP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8MsXyP.gif&h=f83cf594&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/t8MsXyP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ft8MsXyP.gif&h=f83cf594&s=